Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.44,0:00:04.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,入学之后过了将近一个月
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.62,0:00:09.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就像是不断将巨石推向山顶的西绪福斯一样
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.62,0:00:09.22,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（西绪福斯是古希腊科林斯的国王\N由于欺骗了众神  被宙斯判罚死后永远在冥界将山下的巨石推向山顶\N但每当巨石接近山顶时都会滚下去）
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.57,0:00:13.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经完全满足地饱尝了这条徒步登山路线
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.43,0:00:16.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是就在这时  有件仿佛让我搭上性命般的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.84,0:00:21.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我的平常心仿佛8.0级大地震一般动摇的事件发生了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.05,0:00:22.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讨…讨厌啦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.15,0:00:23.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  不
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.89,0:00:25.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该说是「开始了」比较合适吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.74,0:00:30.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有的话自己组建一个就好了！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.84,0:00:31.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,社团啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.19,0:00:33.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要你帮忙
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.08,0:00:36.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名字我刚刚已经想到了！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.31,0:00:38.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,SOS团！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.47,0:00:44.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由稀世的怪人·凉宫春日造成的无限地狱开始了…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.28,0:00:46.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.77,0:00:49.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.81,0:00:51.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我忘记今天要值日了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.92,0:00:54.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要快点到教师办公室去拿班级日志
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.82,0:00:56.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉  我先走了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.56,0:00:59.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,班上明明也是有那种女生的…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.11,0:01:07.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  阿虚  你觉得接下来还需要什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.47,0:01:08.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.23,0:01:12.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还是想要找到谜样的转学生！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.29,0:01:15.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托你说些不会让人觉得不知所云的话吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.06,0:01:18.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是SOS团需要的啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.37,0:01:20.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然还是很想找个谜样的转学生呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.86,0:01:23.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请先告诉我你所谓「谜样」的定义
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.15,0:01:26.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从学期开始到现在已经过了两个月
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.13,0:01:31.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而现在才转学来的人已经拥有足够资格称之为「谜样」了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.73,0:01:32.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不觉得吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.92,0:01:35.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也许是因为老爸突然被调职了呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.34,0:01:37.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  那样实在太不自然了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.75,0:01:40.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对于你来说什么才叫自然？我倒是很想知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.02,0:01:44.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底会不会出现呢？谜样的转学生
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.12,0:01:50.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正对于你来说我的意见不过是耳边风而已吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.98,0:03:27.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,校园里似乎开始流传起我跟春日在密谋什么的谣言
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.22,0:03:30.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说啊  你跟凉宫一起到底在搞些什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.37,0:03:33.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该不会是在谈恋爱吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.15,0:03:35.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝对不是！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.84,0:03:40.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才是最想知道我到底究竟是在做什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.03,0:03:42.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们也有点分寸吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.54,0:03:43.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经不是初中生了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.24,0:03:45.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果把操场弄得无法使用的话
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.04,0:03:47.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞不好会被停学的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.55,0:03:54.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望至少长门有希和朝比奈实玖瑠学姐不要被牵连进去啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.13,0:03:57.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自从SOS团宣告成立以来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.14,0:04:01.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个原本陈设单调的文学社活动室\N开始渐渐出现了些乱七八糟的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.14,0:04:04.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说  你打算住在这里吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.87,0:04:09.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好想要一台电脑呢！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.83,0:04:13.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这个信息化的时代里如果连一台电脑都没有的话
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.84,0:04:15.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是不会被原谅的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.64,0:04:17.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是觉得谁不会原谅啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.31,0:04:19.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么我们去弄一台过来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.25,0:04:21.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂  你想从哪里弄啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.40,0:04:24.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你该不会打算去抢电器行吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.39,0:04:27.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可能！是更近的地方啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.25,0:04:27.25,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}（电脑研究社）
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.58,0:04:30.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们好～
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.50,0:04:34.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我前来征收一台电脑～
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.02,0:04:37.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪个是社长？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.58,0:04:38.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么事吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.59,0:04:43.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会特地跑到电脑研究社来只可能有一件事吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.83,0:04:46.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我电脑  只要一台就可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.30,0:04:48.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？你突然跑过来胡说什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.60,0:04:49.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一台有什么关系嘛！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.06,0:04:51.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们明明有这么多的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.49,0:04:53.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说啊…还有  你们到底是什么人？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.98,0:04:56.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,SOS团团长凉宫春日
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.66,0:04:59.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这两个分别是我的部下一和部下二
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.38,0:05:04.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以你就废话少说快点给我一台
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.74,0:05:07.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凭什么啊！这当然不行了！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.19,0:05:12.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  是这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.80,0:05:15.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么我们也有自己的办法～
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.86,0:05:23.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.50,0:05:29.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想做什么啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.86,0:05:32.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再来一张！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.43,0:05:37.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你到底要做什么！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.83,0:05:39.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿嘿嘿
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.36,0:05:43.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可是很清楚地拍下你性骚扰的照片了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.02,0:05:46.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果不想让这些照片在学校里到处流传的话
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.75,0:05:48.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就乖乖地把电脑交出来！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.96,0:05:49.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你开什么玩笑！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.17,0:05:51.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你强行拉我去摸的！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.88,0:05:52.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是无辜的！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.82,0:05:57.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你觉得有几个人去听你解释呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.40,0:06:02.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在…在这里的各位社员就是我的证人！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.85,0:06:03.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.37,0:06:05.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,社长没做坏事！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.00,0:06:11.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我就说你们所有社员集体**她！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.50,0:06:13.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管怎么说这也太…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.81,0:06:14.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.80,0:06:16.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你给还是不给？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.61,0:06:18.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凉  凉宫同学…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.93,0:06:20.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.19,0:06:33.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要哪台你自己拿走吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.49,0:06:34.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,社长！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.34,0:06:36.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请振作点…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.06,0:06:38.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请打起精神来…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.05,0:06:40.50,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}部长没有做错事…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.12,0:06:41.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么喜剧吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.96,0:06:45.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪一个是最新型号的？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.50,0:06:48.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我凭什么要告诉你！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.36,0:06:53.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶…是那一台
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.83,0:06:59.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天我去电脑专卖店向店员要了最近的新型机种一览表呢～
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.29,0:07:02.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这一台好像没有登在上面呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.63,0:07:07.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这台给我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.37,0:07:09.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等  等一下！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.60,0:07:11.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那一台是上个月刚刚买的…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.24,0:07:16.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿去吧  土匪！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.34,0:07:19.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说得一点没错  的确是土匪
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.26,0:07:21.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  阿虚
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.18,0:07:22.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搬走
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.79,0:07:28.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,于是呢  这样一台最新式的电脑就被抢到手了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.37,0:07:32.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春日在得知文学社没有互联网环境时
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.44,0:07:34.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又叫来了电脑研究会社长和其他人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.48,0:07:36.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在两间活动室之间架设了局域网线
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.78,0:07:40.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并且叫他们帮忙接入了校域内网
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.02,0:07:43.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是所谓的土匪猖獗吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.47,0:07:48.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之  先回家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.09,0:07:57.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朝比奈学姐  你还是不要和这种奇怪的社团扯上关系比较好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.32,0:08:00.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以后还不知道那个家伙会做出些什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.64,0:08:05.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  没关系的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.66,0:08:12.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且你不是也在吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.83,0:08:21.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恐怕这是这个时间平面上的「必然」呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.58,0:08:22.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.09,0:08:26.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且我也很在意长门同学会在这里…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.04,0:08:27.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在意她什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.24,0:08:31.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  没什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.62,0:08:37.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小女子尚未经世事  以后也请多多关照
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.03,0:08:43.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有  请你叫我「实玖瑠」就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.10,0:08:47.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  等待我的下一件事是…？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.21,0:08:50.35,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs32}{\pos(244,5)}架
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.51,0:08:50.45,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs32}{\pos(275,5)}设
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.81,0:08:50.55,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs32}{\pos(300,5)}S
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.11,0:08:50.65,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs32}{\pos(321,5)}O
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.41,0:08:50.75,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs32}{\pos(344,5)}S
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.71,0:08:50.85,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs32}{\pos(368,5)}团
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.01,0:08:50.95,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs32}{\pos(400,5)}的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.31,0:08:51.05,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs32}{\pos(431,5)}网
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.61,0:08:51.15,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs32}{\pos(461,5)}站
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.98,0:08:54.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,于是  这个什么网站你想要谁来做啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.59,0:08:55.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.73,0:08:57.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正你闲得要命  就你做吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.28,0:09:00.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还得去找剩下的社员呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.28,0:09:02.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就在这一两天把它做好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.91,0:09:05.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果没有先做好网页的话
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.79,0:09:07.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么活动都没法开始
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.61,0:09:13.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做网站啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.18,0:09:17.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然说着这种话  但是我却很有兴趣地做了起来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.40,0:09:21.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,电脑研究社已经把几乎所有用得上的软件都安装好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.61,0:09:22.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以做起来倒是很简单
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.33,0:09:25.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就当作是午休时间打发无聊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.95,0:09:29.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倒是要在上面写些什么好呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.85,0:09:34.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管怎么说  我还不知道SOS团到底是个要做什么的社团呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.14,0:09:37.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,长门  你有什么想写上去的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.01,0:09:38.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.24,0:09:44.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然不关我的事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.04,0:09:47.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过她到底能不能好好上课呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.34,0:10:02.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟糕  上课了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.72,0:10:07.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.98,0:10:08.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,借给你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.19,0:10:11.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（海柏安的殒落）
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.19,0:10:11.17,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（Dan Simmons所著的科幻小说\N曾在网上幻想小说数据库(ISFDB)的Top100排名中排行第14）
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.42,0:10:28.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然也没什么好怀疑的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.84,0:10:32.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么我要这样频繁地往活动室跑呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.45,0:10:33.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.28,0:10:36.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是所谓的习性吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.33,0:10:36.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.72,0:10:39.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.08,0:10:43.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过这两个人是不是也很闲啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.25,0:10:45.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然我也没资格说别人…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.88,0:10:48.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凉宫同学呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.61,0:10:51.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁知道  第六节课时就不在了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.64,0:10:55.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,八成又到哪里去抢夺设备了吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.28,0:10:59.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…该不会还会像昨天一样…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.58,0:11:04.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系的  再有这种事的话我一定会全力阻止她的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.14,0:11:07.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗？谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.18,0:11:09.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么就拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.24,0:11:11.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就请交给我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.81,0:11:13.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呀呵～
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.24,0:11:15.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么呀呵啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.20,0:11:21.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首先是这个
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.75,0:11:25.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,SOS团成立宣言及…理念声明？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.81,0:11:28.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后是这个
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.35,0:11:30.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,锵锵锵锵～
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.04,0:11:34.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要穿这个去发传单哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.32,0:11:35.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在哪里啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.53,0:11:38.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,校门口  现在还有很多学生正要回家呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.42,0:11:40.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那要穿什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.63,0:11:41.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是说你啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.21,0:11:43.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是实玖瑠要穿
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.26,0:11:44.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,穿什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.00,0:11:45.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兔女郎！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.61,0:11:48.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个  那个  到底要做什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.14,0:11:50.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了好了  换衣服换衣服！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.85,0:11:51.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不要…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.74,0:11:52.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少废话！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.35,0:11:53.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我脱  给我脱！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.20,0:11:56.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂！凉宫！别太过分了…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.39,0:11:58.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要——！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.69,0:12:00.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要看我——！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.80,0:12:01.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老实点！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.97,0:12:08.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快给我全部脱光——！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.14,0:12:14.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要——！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.37,0:12:17.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至少…让我自己脱…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.51,0:12:20.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  不要——！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.69,0:12:24.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以进来了哦～
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.15,0:12:25.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,简直是个恶人县官
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.68,0:12:30.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样？这样一定大受瞩目！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.84,0:12:32.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样想不受瞩目都不可能吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.01,0:12:33.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,长门不用穿吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.36,0:12:36.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只买了两套而已
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.44,0:12:38.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为是全套的  贵得很呢！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.11,0:12:40.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种东西你是在哪里买的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.87,0:12:41.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,网上订购
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.35,0:12:42.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.81,0:12:44.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么我们走了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.89,0:12:47.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要走了哦  实玖瑠
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.73,0:12:50.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  不  不要…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.55,0:12:53.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走喽～
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.05,0:12:56.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.53,0:13:00.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真的忍不住了…那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.41,0:13:03.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祝你好运了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.39,0:13:19.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉呀呀
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.63,0:13:23.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有体温呢  摸起来温温的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.56,0:13:31.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,SOS团成立宣言及理念声明
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.67,0:13:35.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我SOS团正在广泛收集这世上一切不可思议的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.35,0:13:39.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,过去曾经历过不可思议事情的人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.25,0:13:42.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在正在面临不可思议的现象或谜团的人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.23,0:13:46.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或者将要在不久的将来体验不可思议之事的人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.33,0:13:49.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果有这样的人  就请来找我们进行咨询吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.67,0:13:51.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们会立刻想办法帮你们解决的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.91,0:13:54.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  普通的不可思议事件恕不受理
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.66,0:13:57.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必须是能够把我们吓一跳的不可思议事件才行
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.98,0:13:58.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这一点敬请注意
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.92,0:14:03.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我好像渐渐理解这个社团的存在意义了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.19,0:14:12.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,气死我了！那些白痴老师搞什么鬼啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.32,0:14:13.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太碍事了！太碍事了！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.59,0:14:15.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出什么问题了么？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.94,0:14:16.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,问题大了！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.11,0:14:20.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,传单还没有发到一半  那些老师就跑过来叫停
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.10,0:14:22.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们以为自己是谁啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.75,0:14:26.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看到两个兔女郎在学校的门口发传单
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.43,0:14:28.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算不是老师也会有人来劝阻的！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.36,0:14:30.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,实玖瑠一下子就哭出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.66,0:14:32.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还被带到学生训导室去！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.16,0:14:35.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋手球狂冈部也叫来了！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.62,0:14:37.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都不知道该往哪里看才好了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.89,0:14:41.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的！今天就到此为止！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.88,0:14:42.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,解散！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.75,0:14:47.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要哭到什么时候！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.27,0:14:48.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了！快给我换衣服！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.96,0:14:58.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿虚
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.57,0:15:04.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我嫁不出去了的话  你还会要我吗…？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.40,0:15:11.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这你叫我该说些什么呢  朝比奈学姐
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.06,0:15:15.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的背影就好像高考落榜的重考生
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.48,0:15:19.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或是借钱买下一栋独幢房屋之后  立刻就被炒鱿鱼的上班族一样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.36,0:15:23.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  还有  你怎么也开始叫我那个名字了？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.35,0:15:29.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第二天  凉宫春日的名字就超越了「有名」的等级
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.68,0:15:32.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一跃成为了全校学生的「常识」了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.63,0:15:34.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说阿虚啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.00,0:15:39.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来你也终于成为了\N凉宫春日和她愉快的伙伴们中的一员了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.95,0:15:40.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吵死了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.45,0:15:43.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,更加麻烦的是作为附赠
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.58,0:15:46.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和朝比奈学姐的名字也出现在了传闻中
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.05,0:15:49.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天真是吓了一跳啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.56,0:15:51.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然有兔女郎站在校门口
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.33,0:15:55.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,另外一个人是二年级的朝比奈学姐吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.40,0:15:58.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在你们已经是全校学生瞩目的焦点了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.94,0:16:01.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个「SOS团」到底是什么呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.38,0:16:06.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去问凉宫吧  我可不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.60,0:16:07.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且也不想知道
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.90,0:16:10.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们好像在做很有趣的事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.77,0:16:13.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我觉得那件事做得有点过分了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.45,0:16:18.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那一天  朝比奈学姐请假了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.79,0:16:20.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么一封邮件都没有收到啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.86,0:16:22.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都作了这么大力度的宣传了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.52,0:16:26.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就因为那宣传  现在已经没有想和这个社团扯上关系的好事之徒了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.69,0:16:29.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然我不否认的确有超群的瞩目度
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.85,0:16:33.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？实玖瑠她…今天请假了？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.73,0:16:35.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也许不会再回来了！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.64,0:16:37.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望别对她留下精神伤害…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.95,0:16:40.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难得我准备了新的服装…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.07,0:16:42.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己穿吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.54,0:16:44.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我当然也会穿啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.47,0:16:47.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是实玖瑠不在的话太无聊了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.65,0:16:49.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让长门穿也可以啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.67,0:16:51.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她一定会二话不说就穿起来的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.90,0:16:53.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,另外我倒是也很想看到会是什么样子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.15,0:17:00.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,SOS团刚刚建立怎么就遭受挫折了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.77,0:17:03.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家是不是都不愿意把自己的经历说出来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.38,0:17:04.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道想自己独占吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.33,0:17:06.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说  春日啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.56,0:17:10.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种县级公立高中  怎么可能会有个阴暗角落不断冒出不可思议的谜团
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.87,0:17:15.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且还多到随便找个人问「有吗」  就会回答「有」那么多的程度啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.24,0:17:17.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你明白了吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.61,0:17:19.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实你也应该知道的吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.27,0:17:23.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是因为那些不停蠢动无处发泄的年轻意气
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.35,0:17:26.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,导致的不爽心情把你控制住  引导了你的行动罢了吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.04,0:17:28.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也该清醒一下了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.99,0:17:32.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赶快去抓个帅哥一起放学回家
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.54,0:17:34.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后星期天一起去看个电影吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.09,0:17:38.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后加入个运动社团尽情地大干一场吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.54,0:17:41.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以你的资质  一定马上就能够作为正式选手而活跃啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.87,0:17:42.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回去了！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.14,0:17:53.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  我也回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.42,0:17:56.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.95,0:17:57.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.85,0:18:00.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,书
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.04,0:18:02.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…不  还没有呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.49,0:18:04.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要不要先还给你？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.15,0:18:06.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用还我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.98,0:18:10.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是她还真是每句话都不超过稿纸一行的长度啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.39,0:18:12.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天记得看
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.74,0:18:15.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回家后马上看
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.04,0:18:18.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.57,0:18:37.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（晚上七点  在光阳园车站前的公园等你）
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.57,0:18:38.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（等你）
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.70,0:18:41.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？阿虚你去哪？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.36,0:18:42.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,车站前
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.32,0:18:44.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不许一边吃东西一边说话
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.45,0:18:59.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天来…也可以吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.13,0:19:03.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该不会你昨天也在这里等着吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.94,0:19:06.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么要特地把我叫到这里来？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.16,0:19:08.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这边
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.01,0:19:09.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.25,0:19:31.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,家里人呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.04,0:19:32.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不在
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.64,0:19:36.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃  我也看出来不在了…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.29,0:19:38.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出门了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.02,0:19:41.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从一开始就只有我一个人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.20,0:19:43.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你一个人住吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.91,0:19:44.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.23,0:19:47.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么…有什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.17,0:19:53.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喝吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.61,0:19:59.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好喝？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.83,0:20:03.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.63,0:20:30.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肚子都涨了…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.82,0:20:32.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.94,0:20:36.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请问你现在能不能把叫我到这里来的理由告诉我呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.89,0:20:42.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「在学校不能说的事」究竟是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.06,0:20:50.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是关于凉宫春日
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.21,0:20:55.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.32,0:20:59.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想告诉你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.97,0:21:04.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凉宫和你…怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.61,0:21:10.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我无法将其准确地用语言表述出来
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.09,0:21:14.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,传递的信息也许会发生偏差
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.38,0:21:15.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.88,0:21:17.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听我说
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.05,0:21:23.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凉宫春日和我不是普通人类
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.10,0:21:26.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个我或多或少能看得出来啦…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.28,0:21:28.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是这个意思
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.11,0:21:35.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我并不是指性格上没有普遍性
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.10,0:21:37.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而是如字面所说
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.88,0:21:43.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她和我都不能被称为是和像你一样大多数的「人类」一样
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.97,0:21:49.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而由统管这个银河系的信息统合思念体制造出来的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.60,0:21:54.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对有机生命体接触用人形终端界面
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.56,0:21:56.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.04,0:21:59.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.47,0:22:06.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用通俗的用语来说明  就是相当于「外星人」的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.61,0:22:11.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,外…星人？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.15,0:03:35.25,neta,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,[这种时候如果慌慌张张地否认\N或者吃惊得喷饭的话100%是在交往或者快要开始交往了…\N看来阿虚和团长之间还早呢]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.13,0:04:01.67,neta,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,[「现在室内角落摆着一座不知从哪里拿来的可携式衣架、\N热水壶和陶杯、茶碗、没有MD功能的CD录放两用收音机、\N单层冰箱、录音机、陶锅、水壶以及各种食器。」]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.39,0:04:27.04,neta,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,[注意她并没说不是要抢，而只是地点不同而已…]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.83,0:04:46.15,neta,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,[怎么可能有为了这种事来电脑研究社的！…阿囧为啥没吐这句？]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.85,0:06:05.82,neta,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,[怎么把搞电脑的描写得这么弱气= =\N（以上为搞电脑的某人的吐槽）]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.00,0:06:11.23,neta,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,[脑内补完协力：根据小说，消音部分的词是“轮○”]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.09,0:08:26.69,neta,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,[…嗯？1096×大明神？…貌似不错的样子…]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.62,0:08:37.03,neta,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,[经典的新婚妻子在初夜时打招呼的语句…]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.60,0:08:45.25,neta,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,[阿囧的囧脸…]
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.24,0:09:47.25,neta,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,[老师已经长教训不会再点她回答问题了吧…或者被“设定”成那样…]
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.33,0:10:36.92,neta,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,[这是这个时间平面的必然…]
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.91,0:14:12.16,neta,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,[「三十分钟后，精疲力尽的朝比奈回来了。…\N（朝比奈）趴在桌子上，然后肩膀开始剧烈地抖动起来。\N看来，她连换衣服的力气都没有了。\N…于是，我脱下运动外套，盖在她白皙而不停颤抖的背上。\N不断哭泣的少女和对外界完全没反应的读书虫，\N再加上慌张到不行的我，将室内气氛搞到最低点。」]
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.06,0:15:19.68,neta,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,[刻薄的家伙…]
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.38,0:16:06.28,neta,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,[去问你顶头上司吧。虽然我知道你和她\N相处得不好，但是只要诚心请教她还是会告诉你的。]
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.90,0:16:53.94,neta,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,[阿囧(2929****)0:17:02\N另外我倒是也很想看到会是什么样子\N茶々丸MK-Ⅱ(40691****)0:17:05\N+1]
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.57,0:18:37.57,neta,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,[任务物品：通向不可思议的请柬]
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.11,0:18:54.88,neta,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,[「她真是个存在感稀薄的女生。\N像她这样静静地坐在公园里，不知情的人可能会以为她是幽灵耶！」]
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.40,0:19:23.37,neta,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,[「这大概是3LDK的房子吧？而且还在车站前，相信房价一定很贵。\N但是为何屋内感觉好像没人住过？」]
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.57,0:19:27.06,neta,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,[「除了刚刚经过的客厅摆了张暖被桌之外，其他什么都没有。\N没有窗帘，十张榻榻米大小的木制地板上也没有铺地毯，\N露出茶色的木纹。」]
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.34,0:19:51.92,neta,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,[「长门就像突然想起来似的倒了一杯茶，然后把它推到我面前」]
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.71,0:20:02.63,neta,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,[最近的机器人（？）都好会泡茶哦…]
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.45,0:20:05.83,neta,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,[「当我喝完热茶将杯子放在桌上时，长门立刻再替我倒满。」]
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.45,0:20:12.83,neta,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,[「既然她都倒了，我也只能把它喝掉。」]
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.95,0:20:19.83,neta,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,[「在我喝完时，她又替我倒了第三杯。」]
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.82,0:20:36.73,neta,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,[「最后陶壶空了，长门起身一副打算再去续壶的模样。\N我见状连忙阻止她。」]
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.60,0:21:54.55,neta,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,[因为是对有机生命体接触用的，所以才叫“有希”么…]


